    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Igitur fidelium nostrorum presentium ac futurorum noverit multitudo quoniam
                        pro salutem animarum nostrarum seu <rs key="#familyOf">parentum</rs>
                        nostrorum <persName key="#familyOf" ref="#people/3061">Askitini</persName>
                        et <persName key="#familyOf" ref="#people/4237">Roberti</persName>, quam
                        etiam et ob animam magne recordationis <rs key="#uncle/auntOf">avunculi</rs>
                        nostri <rs key="#Consul/hypatos">consulis</rs> et <rs key="#Marquis/duke"
                            >ducis</rs>
                        <persName key="#Marquis/duke #Consul/hypatos #uncle/auntOf"
                            ref="#people/3060">Raynulfi</persName>, <rs key="#Intercessory">per
                            interventum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Intercessory" ref="#people/4238">Landulfi Riche</persName>
                        et <persName key="#Intercessory" ref="#people/4200">Pandulfi
                            Guale</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/4239"
                            >Citro</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">vice principis</rs>, per hoc videlicet
                        principale scriptum damus, tradimus, concedimus et confirmamus in <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName> sito in <placeName ref="#places/109">Monte
                            Casino</placeName>, in quo domnus <persName
                            key="#Cardinals #Abbots #Personal_rank" ref="#people/2421"
                            >Desiderius</persName> divina ordinante clementia <rs
                            key="#Personal_rank">venerabilis</rs> ac religiosus <rs key="#Cardinals"
                            >cardinalis</rs> et <rs key="#Abbots">abbas</rs> regimen tenere videtur,
                            <rs key="#Churches">aecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3031">Sancti Benedicti Piczoli</orgName> sitam
                        in <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/173">Capua</placeName>, non longe
                        ab <rs key="#Mother_churches">ecclesia archiepiscopatus</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/3045">sanctorum
                            martyrum Stephani et Agathes</orgName>, cum <rs key="#Churches"
                            >aecclesiis</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters">aquis</rs> et universis
                        pertinentiis suis. Nec non et <rs key="#Churches">aecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches #Slave"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3058">Sancti Petri qui dicitur ad
                            Scaphati</orgName>, sitam in <rs key="#City_territory">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities #City_territory" ref="#places/2350"><geogName
                                key="#City_territory" ref="#estates/3074"
                            >Neapolitano</geogName></placeName>, cum <rs key="#Churches"
                            >ecclesiis</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">terris</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Slave_labour #Slave">servis</rs> et universis pertinentiis suis,
                        ad possessionem et proprietatem prephati monasterii et predicti domni
                        abbatis et eius successorum, ad habendum et possidendum et faciendum
                        regulariter omnia quae eis placuerint, remota omni inquietudine vel
                        molestatione cuiuscumque comitis, iudicis, castaldei, sculdahiset omnium
                        mortalium personae. Quod si quelibet persona hominum magna vel parva contra
                        hanc nostri precepti firmitatem agere presumpserit aut eius violator in
                        quocumque fieri temptaverit, sciat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri
                            purissimi libras quinquaginta</rs>; medietatem nostre camere et
                        medietatem prephato monasterio et predicto domno Desiderio <rs
                            key="#Personal_rank">reverentissimo</rs> cardinali atque abbati suisque
                        successoribus. Et post solutam paenam, huius nostre concessionis pagina
                        munita, firma et stabilis maneat in perpetuum. Ut autem haec nostra
                        concessio, datio atque confirmatio firmius credatur et diligentius ab
                        omnibus observetur, manu nostra propria corroboravimus et nostri sigilli
                        impressione iussimus insigniri. (M) Ex iussione prephate serenissime
                        potestatis, scriptum per manu <persName key="#Writer #Judge"
                            ref="#people/3064">Iohannis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs>, anno dominicae incarnationis millesimo
                        septuagesimo secundo, mense augusto, indictione decima. In anno <rs
                            key="#Princeps">principatus</rs> ipsius domni <persName key="#Princeps"
                            ref="#people/3001">Richardi</persName>, Deo annuente quarto decimo. </ab>
